697
00:51:23,977 --> 00:51:24,978
Sungguh?

698
00:51:26,938 --> 00:51:28,481
Apakah itu mungkin?

699
00:51:32,735 --> 00:51:33,611
KESEPAKATAN DAMAI

700
00:51:33,695 --> 00:51:34,904
FIRMA HUKUM SONG & KIM

