705
00:51:48,042 --> 00:51:50,628
Dia tak pernah serakah soal uang.

706
00:51:50,712 --> 00:51:52,046
Dia ingin bermain biola.

707
00:51:52,130 --> 00:51:52,964
Dan...

708
00:51:53,506 --> 00:51:54,382
Kebebasan.

709
00:51:55,550 --> 00:51:56,634
Pak Ko

710
